    <p class="pp_text">Under the GDPR, you have the following rights regarding your personal data:</p>
    <h4>7.1 Right of Access</h4>
    <p class="pp_text">Request a copy of the personal data we hold about you.</p>
    <h4>7.2 Right of Rectification</h4>
    <p class="pp_text">Request corrections to inaccurate or incomplete data.</p>
    <h4>7.3 Right to Erasure</h4>
    <p class="pp_text">Request the deletion of your personal data:</p>
    <ul class="pp_text">
        <li>Immediately, if you delete your user account.</li>
        <li>If the data is no longer needed for its intended purposes.</li>
    </ul>
    <h4>7.4 Right to Data Portability</h4>
    <p class="pp_text">Request your data in a readable and transferable format.</p>
    <h4>7.5 Right to Object</h4>
    <p class="pp_text">
        Object to the processing of your data in certain cases, such as for marketing or analysis purposes.
    </p>
    <p class="pp_text">
        To exercise your rights, contact us at 'BlocknBeyond@yopmail.com'. Proof of identity may be required to ensure the security of your information.
    </p>
</div>

